  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "All other widgets set the page to 0, only configure doesn't as many parameters you could change don't need to reset the page. I recommend you also have a look at useMenu, useRefinementList instead of useConfigure, as it will play nice with eg. routing too.\r\n\r\nAs you've found the solution and this is by design I'll close the issue now.",
